  "texts": [
    "Rapid and accurate detection of plant diseases is crucial for increasing agricultural productivity.",
    "Traditionally, agriculture professionals rely on manual diagnosis to identify plant abnormalities caused by disease (Al-Hiary et al., 2011).",
    "However, this approach requires significant human and material resources and is not realistic (Ngugi et al., 2021).",
    "In response to these challenges, the use of image processing technology for automated diagnosis of plant diseases has garnered increased attention (Boulent et al., 2019).",
    "In recent years, there has been remarkable progress in image classification due to the emergence of deep learning and neural networks."
  ],
